&lt;p&gt;You will join a small, senior team and work directly alongside our Finance &amp;amp; Legal Lead. Your key stakeholders will be the leadership team, as well as our Finance, Operations, and Commercial functions across a globally distributed organisation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Legal Counsel, you will be Kayzen’s primary legal owner across four core areas. You will operate as a trusted business partner — not just a gatekeeper — and are expected to move fast, apply sound commercial judgment, and help the business scale without unnecessary legal friction.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
